Parkland to acquire Yukon marketing firm . Parkland Industries Ltd said on Thursday it agreed to buy Whitehorse , Yukon - based Northern Petroleum for C $ 1 . 5 million . Parkland said the price would include deferred payments of C $ 350 , 000 and the assumption of a C $ 2250 , 000 real estate mortgage . Northern Petroleum operates seven independent gas stations , a retail heating oil business , contract fuel service and a trucking arm . The acquisition was expected to add about C $ 500 , 000 to Parkland ' s pre - tax earnings over the next year , it said . The deal was to be effective on February 1 , 1997 . ( ( Reuters Calgary Bureau ( 403 ) 531 - 1624 ) ) 
